d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825e54fb8207db6d8a26c7829deb9889a65b79a2","tid":370971,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實個人要幾自卑先要上嚟扮曬野扮窮其實想炫耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知"},{"pid":"f75e9a65fe08a6e539a3633c7aac953b42ea9231","tid":370971,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"睇你點睇<br />\n要搵食算唔算窮撚?"},{"pid":"11dc5e98b8a3f0589be0d1836471d18e4c3a55e6","tid":370971,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"仲問！連登個個月入十萬"},{"pid":"28e167ae79eb497c05f22099027be70c1c12821c","tid":370971,"uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:00:41.000Z","msg":"係好撚窮"},{"pid":"47b30fff6c6029bd357239fc543e846d09ea0731","tid":370971,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:01:53.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"906477e1188b80face6323f6f754d8192551d1b1","tid":370971,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"一至二人家庭20萬就ok, 4人先20萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b022bf642d73f35e7aebd3288adc48bd71f2f4d","tid":370971,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:19:22.000Z","msg":"講真 得果廿萬 我係你就冇面上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1fcf0bc7a7326ba78bf23686e78fd7aaf95b84","tid":370971,"uid":51369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:20:02.000Z","msg":"屌你廿萬食餐飯都無撚左 點夠生活呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.g